(1, '1) What is Opportunity \"4\"?', '1-what-is-opportunity-4', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1) What is Opportunity &quot;4&quot;?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Opportunity &quot;4&quot; is a software put together to help common people, everyday people who are trying to make the two ends meet, who are trying to put food on the table of the family ...... to get helped and in turn help other people to find this opportunity and free them financially! Selfish people cannot succeed in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;! The more you share Opportunity &quot;4&quot;, the more users subscribe under you, the more benefits you get!</p>', '2017-10-16 14:19:30', '2018-07-04 03:35:00', 'en'),
(31, '10) How Opportunity \"4\" pays your monthly fees?', '10-how-opportunity-4-pays-your-monthly-fees', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>10) How Opportunity &quot;4&quot; pays your monthly fees?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Opportunity &quot;4&quot; pays your monthly fees from the time you have 10 subcribers in your team, no matter what level! (from level 1 to level 4). Why? Because for 10 subscribers in your team, the system returns to you as benefit every month the amount of the monthly fee. You will begin making money in the system from the 11th subscriber in your group. The golden beginning in Opportunity &quot;4&quot; is to bring 20 subscribers in the system in your very 1st month, in the month you enter the system. Why? Please, read the question &quot;How to never pay fees in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;?&quot;</p>', NULL, NULL, 'en'),
(6, '4) How to NEVER pay fees in Opportunity \"4\"?', '4-how-to-never-pay-fees-in-opportunity-4', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4) How to NEVER pay fees in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To never pay fees in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;, you HAVE to bring 20 active subscribers into the system before the end of the month you enter Opportunity &quot;4&quot;! These 20 active subcribers might not be brought into the system by you only, as long as you have 20 active subcribers in your group, no matter what level they locate (from level 1 to 4), you are fine!&nbsp;Why? The percentage of the fees of the 20 active subscribers in your group will amount 2 times the monthly fees. Then at the end of the month,&nbsp;the system reimburses the fees you paid to enter the Opportunity &quot;4&quot; and you have another monthly fee for the next month fees payment. As you can see, it is like you never pay fees in the system because you are reimbursed the one you paid to enter the system and are given another monthly fee for the next month!</p>', '2018-07-05 04:01:20', '2018-09-11 22:27:10', 'en'),
(2, '2) Why Opportunity \"4\"?', '2-why-opportunity-4', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2) Why Opportunity &quot;4&quot;?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Opportunity &quot;4&quot; is primarily created to help poor continents, specially Africa. We do believe at Opportunity &quot;4&quot; that all over the world, in both poor and rich countries, people have &quot;dreams&quot; and talents but these get put on hold or lost because of financial means. We believe that poor people from the poor areas of the world are, in no way, lesser than people from rich areas, what makes the difference is opportunities, the advantage people in rich areas have on people in poor areas of the world is rich areas have more opportunities than poor areas. To be born in a poor area&nbsp;is not a choice, it is a pure hazard, it is not even a God decision like some people might believe it, you find it out at birth! The same way you don&#39;t choose your parents and country, the same way you are not in control of your place of birth, you cannot even change it at your birth, you might leave it if you choose to but you cannot change.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Opportunity &quot;4&quot; was created to give to poor areas of the world an opportunity their birth area might not give to them: easy financial means. We believe this will allow them to pursue their dreams and work on their talents we are so convinced they have.</p>', '2018-07-04 03:21:48', '2018-10-31 07:21:42', 'en'),
(7, '5) What is an active subscriber?', '5-what-is-an-active-subscriber', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5) What is an active subscriber?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>An active subcriber is the subscriber who pays the monthly fees on time. You are only paid your benefits at the end of the month if you are active.</p>', '2018-07-05 04:05:11', '2018-09-11 22:26:52', 'en'),
(8, '6) Does Opportunity \"4\" involve sale?', '6-does-opportunity-4-involve-sale', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6) Does Opportunity &quot;4&quot; involve sale?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>No! You don&#39;t have to sell anything in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;. The only thing you need to do is to share this opportunity, the more you share it, the bigger your benefits become!</p>', '2018-07-05 17:45:36', '2018-09-11 22:25:12', 'en'),
(9, '7) What is multiple accounts in Opportunity \"4\"?', '7-what-is-multiple-accounts-in-opportunity-4', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7) What is multiple accounts in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We allow you to have multiple accounts in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;. Why? It is to help you have access to unlimited rewards.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In Opportunity &quot;4&quot;, we have some challenges for our subscribers, when they hit them, we reward them.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Now we have 3 challenges in every account rewarded&nbsp;with 3 rewards. The more accounts you have, the more chances you have to have more rewards if you hit these challenges.&nbsp;This helps you do more in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;.</p>', '2018-07-05 18:05:58', '2018-09-11 22:25:47', 'en'),
(11, '9) What are the challenges that we have in Opportunity \"4\"?', '9-what-are-the-challenges-that-we-have-in-opportunity-4', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>9) What are the challenges that we have in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>These are the challenges we have in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;? Please <a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/the-3-opportunity-4-challenges-and-their-rewards\">click here</a>!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For an explanation in a video, please&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/user-academy/view/48\">click here</a>!</p>', '2018-07-05 23:27:17', '2018-09-11 22:26:29', 'en'),
(45, '1) Qu\'est-ce que l\'Opportunit√© \"4\"?', '1-qu-est-ce-que-l-opportunit-4', '<p><br></p><p>1) Qu\'est-ce que l\'Opportunit√© \"4\"?<br>Opportunity \"4\" est un logiciel con√ßu pour aider les gens ordinaires, les gens ordinaires qui essaient de joindre les deux bouts chaque jour, qui essaient de mettre de la nourriture sur la table de la famille ...... pour √™tre aid√© et √† tour aider les autres √† trouver cette Opportunit√© et les lib√©rer financi√®rement! Les personnes √©go√Østes ne peuvent pas r√©ussir dans Opportunity \"4\"! Plus vous partagez l\'opportunit√© \"4\", plus nombreux sont les utilisateurs qui s\'abonnent sous vous, plus vous y b√©n√©ficiez d\'avantage!</p><p><br></p>', NULL, NULL, 'fr'),
(46, '2) Pourquoi l\'Opportunit√© \"4\"?', '2-pourquoi-l-opportunit-4', '<p>2) Pourquoi l&#39;Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot;?<br />\r\nL&#39;Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot; est principalement cr&eacute;&eacute;e pour aider les continents pauvres, en particulier l&rsquo;Afrique. Nous pensons, &agrave; l&#39;Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot;, que partout dans le monde, dans les pays riches comme dans les pays pauvres, les gens ont des &quot;r&ecirc;ves&quot; et des talents, mais ceux-ci sont laiss&eacute;s non r&eacute;alis&eacute;s ou perdus par manque de moyens financiers. Nous pensons que les pauvres des r&eacute;gions pauvres du monde ne sont en aucun cas inf&eacute;rieurs &agrave; ceux des r&eacute;gions riches. Ce qui fait la diff&eacute;rence, ce sont les opportunit&eacute;s qui s&#39;offrent &agrave; eux. L&#39;avantage que les habitants des r&eacute;gions riches ont sur les habitants des r&eacute;gions pauvres du monde est ce qu&#39;ils ont plus d&#39;opportunit&eacute;s que les zones pauvres. Na&icirc;tre dans une r&eacute;gion pauvre n&#39;est pas un choix, c&#39;est un pur hazard, ce n&#39;est m&ecirc;me pas une volont&eacute; divine, comme certaines personnes pourraient le croire, vous le d&eacute;couvrez &agrave; la naissance! De la m&ecirc;me mani&egrave;re que vous ne choisissez pas vos parents et votre pays, de la m&ecirc;me mani&egrave;re vous ne contr&ocirc;lez pas votre lieu de naissance, vous ne pouvez m&ecirc;me pas le changer &agrave; votre naissance, vous pouvez le laisser si vous le souhaitez mais vous ne pouvez pas le changer.....<br />\r\nL&#39;Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot; a &eacute;t&eacute; cr&eacute;&eacute;e pour donner aux r&eacute;gions pauvres du monde une opportunit&eacute; que leur r&eacute;gion de naissance ne leur offrirait peut-&ecirc;tre pas: des moyens financiers faciles. Nous pensons que cela leur permettra de poursuivre leurs r&ecirc;ves et de mettre &agrave; profit leurs talents que nous sommes tellement convaincus qu&#39;ils ont!.</p>', NULL, NULL, 'fr'),
(48, '8) Why taxes are not included in commissions calculations?', '8-why-taxes-are-not-included-in-commissions-calculations', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>8) Why we don&#39;t mention the taxes in our calculations of the commissions?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We don&#39;t mention or use the taxes with the base fees in the calculation of subscribers commissions besauce taxes go the government, we don&#39;t pocket these taxes as company.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We do know that we need to pay these taxes for the goverment to continue doing or delivering the important public services we dearly need. Don&#39;t tell me you don&#39;t know these important services! Ok, let me refresh your mind: Government creates for us schools, hospitals, makes roads ect... things and services we cannot afford on ourselves. Taxes have to be paid for these important&nbsp;things to be taken care of by the government.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>And when you pay taxes, you don&#39;t claim them back unless you are in USA where some fractions of the taxes are clained at the end of the year by some qualified workers if you don&#39;t fall into the category where they ask you to pay more money at the end of the year.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Conclusion: Taxes go to the government, we don&#39;t packet them, it is why we don&#39;t includ them in the calculation of the suscribers commissions.</p>', NULL, NULL, 'en'),
(47, '5) Qu\'est-ce qu\'un abonn√© actif?', '5-qu-est-ce-qu-un-abonn-actif', '<p>5) Qu&#39;est-ce qu&#39;un abonn&eacute; actif?<br />\r\nUn abonn&eacute; actif est l&rsquo;abonn&eacute; qui paie les frais mensuels &agrave; temps &agrave; la fin du mois. Vos commissions ne vous sont vers&eacute;es &agrave; la fin du mois que si vous &ecirc;tes actif.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, 'fr'),
(32, '10) Commentaire Opportunit√© \"4\" r√®gle vos frais mensuels?', '10-commentaire-opportunit-4-r-gle-vos-frais-mensuels', '<p>10) Commentaire Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot; r&egrave;gle vos frais mensuels?<br />\r\nOpportunity &quot;4&quot; paie vos frais mensuels &agrave; partir du moment o&ugrave; vous avez 10 abonn&eacute;s dans votre &eacute;quipe, quel que soit votre niveau! (du niveau 1 au niveau 4). Pourquoi? Parce que pour 10 membres de votre &eacute;quipe, le syst&egrave;me vous renvoie chaque mois le montant des frais mensuels. Vous commencerez &agrave; gagner de l&#39;argent dans le syst&egrave;me &agrave; partir du 11e abonn&eacute; de votre groupe. Le bon d&eacute;but dans Opportunity &quot;4&quot; consiste &agrave; amener 20 abonn&eacute;s dans le syst&egrave;me d&egrave;s le premier mois, le mois o&ugrave; vous entrez dans le syst&egrave;me. Pourquoi? S&#39;il vous pla&icirc;t, voir la question sur &quot;Comment ne jamais payer de frais dans Opportunity &quot;4&quot;!&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, 'fr'),
(33, '3) How to register on Opportunity \"4\"?', '3-how-to-register-on-opportunity-4', '<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>3) How to register on Opportunity &quot;4&quot;?<br />\r\nTo sign up for opportunity &quot;4&quot;, follow these <a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/distributor?id=2\">instructions</a>!</div>', NULL, NULL, 'en'),
(23, '4) Comment ne JAMAIS payer de frais dans l\'opportunit√© \"4\"?', '4-comment-ne-jamais-payer-de-frais-dans-l-opportunit-4', '<p><a name=\"4) Comment ne JAMAIS payer de frais dans l\'Opportunit√© \"></a></p>\r\n\r\n<div><a name=\"4) Comment ne JAMAIS payer de frais dans l\'Opportunit√© \">4) Comment ne JAMAIS payer de frais dans l&#39;opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot;?</a></div>\r\n\r\n<div><a name=\"4) Comment ne JAMAIS payer de frais dans l\'Opportunit√© \"> Pour ne jamais payer de frais dans l&#39;Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot;, vous devez amener 20 abonn&eacute;s actifs dans le syst&egrave;me avant la fin du mois durant lequel vous entrez dans l&#39;Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot;! Ces 20 abonn&eacute;s actifs peuvent ne pas &ecirc;tre introduits dans le syst&egrave;me par vous m&ecirc;me, tant que vous avez 20 abonn&eacute;s actifs dans votre groupe, quel que soit le niveau ils se trouvent (du niveau 1 au niveau 4), vous &ecirc;tes bien! Pourquoi? Le pourcentage des frais des 20 abonn&eacute;s actifs de votre groupe sera &eacute;gal &agrave; 2 fois les frais mensuels. Ainsi, &agrave; la fin du mois, le syst&egrave;me rembourse les frais que vous avez pay&eacute;s pour entrer dans l&#39;Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot; et vous disposez d&#39;un autre frais mensuel pour le paiement des frais du mois suivant. Comme vous pouvez le constater, c&#39;est comme si vous n&#39;aviez jamais pay&eacute; de frais dans le syst&egrave;me, car nous vous remboursons les frais que vous avez pay&eacute; pour entrer dans le syst&egrave;me et vous recevez un autre frais mensuel pour le mois suivant!</a></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>', NULL, NULL, 'fr'),
(53, '17) Do you know you are an entrepreneur when you register in Opportunity \"4\"?', '17-do-you-know-you-are-an-entrepreneur-when-you-register-in-opportunity-4', '<p>17) Do you know you are an entrepreneur when you register in Opportunity \"4\"?</p><p>Many of you don‚Äôt know you become an entrepreneur when you register in Opportunity ‚Äú4‚Äù! Yes, you are an entrepreneur when you register on Opportunity ‚Äú4‚Äù! You have created a company from the time you put your information in Opportunity 4!&nbsp;</p><p>As you earn the huge monthly \"Opportunity 4\" commissions, we train you as an entrepreneur by showing you how to run your business once you become a member of Opportunity \"4\".</p><p>This training is designed to show you how to maximize your commissions in Opportunity \"4\", how to manage your business Opportunity \"4\", how to think and behave as an entrepreneur, how to develop your own business ideas and opportunities, how to pursue your dreams and develop your talents and get you started!&nbsp;</p><p>As you can see, this program takes beginners and turns them into entrepreneurs and finance them!</p><p>We have 2 important features on our sites that are very important for you as entrepreneur:&nbsp;<br>1) A&nbsp;page where you can expose your business to your potentiential subscribers and tell them why they should join your group, why they should work with you. This page also helps you&nbsp;connect to your subscribers on social media. Use it fully!<br>2) A message center that allows you to be in communication with your subscribers. This is vital for your group because to coach the members of your group you need to communicate with them and it is appropriate if it is done within Opportunity \"4\"! Use this message center fully to advance your business within Opportunity \"4\"!</p><p>Do you know that if you have means, you should have an office as businessman? Specially if you want to lead in Opportunity \"4\", you need an office with all its ingredients to help your subscribers. You will &nbsp;meet people who will need your help to start in Opportunity \"4\", you need to invite them into your&nbsp;office to help them! As an entrepreneur, to be performent, you need an office!</p><p><br></p>', NULL, NULL, 'en'),
(25, '6) Vend-on quelque chose dans l‚ÄôOpportunit√© \"4\"?', '6-vend-on-quelque-chose-dans-l-opportunit-4', '<p><a name=\"6) Vend-on quelque chose dans l‚ÄôOpportunit√© \"></a></p>\r\n\r\n<div><a name=\"6) Vend-on quelque chose dans l‚ÄôOpportunit√© \">6) Vend-on quelque chose dans l&rsquo;Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot;?</a></div>\r\n\r\n<div><a name=\"6) Vend-on quelque chose dans l‚ÄôOpportunit√© \"> Non! Vous n&#39;avez rien &agrave; vendre dans l&#39;Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot;. La seule chose que vous devez faire est de partager cette opportunit&eacute;, plus vous la partagez, plus vos commissions deviennent importantes!</a></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>', NULL, NULL, 'fr'),
