(40, '13) How to earn the $842 100 at the end of the 5th month?', '13-how-to-earn-the-842-100-at-the-end-of-the-5th-month', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>13) How to earn the 842 100 US dollars&nbsp;at the end of the 5th month? It is by applying Rule 20/20. How?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Applying Rule 20/20 means that after registration, you have to subscribe 20 people under you through your affiliate link preferrably in your 1st month. While you are subscribing each of your 1st 20 people, you must ask them to apply Rule 20/20 too, they have to subscribe into the system, each of them, &nbsp;in their 1st 30 days 20 people through their affiliate links and ask their subscribers to do the same, preferrably, in their 1st 30 days.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In conclusion, aqpplying Rule 20/20 in Opportunity &quot;4&quot; means each subscriber must subscribe into the system 20 people, preferrably in the 1st 30 days and ask those 20 people to do the same in the 1st 30 days and pass the message and the training to their subscribers too.<br />\r\nIf this is done, what happens?&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>By subscribing into the system 20 people in your 1st 30 days, even if you stop subscribing people into the system but you apply Rule 20/20, at the end of the second month you must have 400 people in your account. By the end of the 3rd month you must have 8000 people in your account. By the end of the 4th month, you must have 160 000 people in your account. If in your group everybody pays their monthly fees regularly in the system, we pay you at the end of every month 40% of the total of the fees collected in your group. Because we have 4 levels of benefit in every group, we pay you 10% of the total of the fees at every level, this is the way you earn $842 100&nbsp;at the end of the 5th month.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As you can see it, that amount is a strict minimum when you strictly apply Rule 20/20. Imagine that after you bring into the system 20 people and ask them to subscribe also 20 people into the system