(41, '14) How to succeed quickly in Opportunity \"4\"?', '14-how-to-succeed-quickly-in-opportunity-4', '<p>14) What is the secret of a Rapid Success in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is applying Rule 20/20. The Rule 20/20 is a very important rule in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;. How it works? Why applying it helps you grow quickly in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Rule 20/20, simply put, means:<br />\r\n1) to bring into the system 20 subcribers under you through your affiliate link preferably during your 1st 30 days in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;.<br />\r\n2) to tell your subscribers to bring into the system 20 subscribers through their affiliate links preferably in their 1st 30 days in Opportunity &quot;4&quot; and make sure they know that they must pass the same message to their subscribers.&nbsp;<br />\r\n1) make sure everybody in your group pays their fees monthly. Why this is very important? This is very important because your monthly commissions come from the monthly fees the subcribers in your group pay every month. We pay you 40% of the total of the monthly fees of the subscribers at the 4 levels of your group. Your monthly commissions are not based on the number of the subscribers in your group, they are rather based on the number of the subscribers in your group who&nbsp;pay their monthly fees.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>DNAsbook Digital Marketing is a company that trains its subscribers&nbsp;in entrepreneurship and&nbsp;finances them. To participate into this program, there is a monthly fee to pay. The financing comes from the 40% we pay you from the fees of the subscribers in your group.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Why Rule 20/20 helps you succeed quickly in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;? It is because of the 4 levels of benefits. Why 4 levels of benefits in Opportunity 4? It is to help subscribers maximize their monthly commissions by doing just a small effort by bringing into the system 20 subscribers. If these subscribers also bring into the system