\n<div>Want to take the money cash? Please, see conditions!</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>3) Rule 300/90 for just one month</div>\r\n\r\n<div>4) 2 430 000 x 90 = 218 700 000; 218 700 000 x $50 = $10 935 000 000; $10 935 000 000 x 10% = $1 093 500 000</div>\r\n\r\n<div>3) 27 000 x 90 = 2 430 000; 2 430 000 x $50 = $121 500 000; $121 500 000 x 10% = $12 150 000</div>\r\n\r\n<div>2) 300 x 90 = 27 000; 27 000 x $50 = $1 350 000; $1 350 000 x 10% = $135 000</div>\r\n\r\n<div>1) 300; 300 x $50 = $15 000; $15 000 x 10% = $1 500</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Total: $ 1 500 + $135 000 + $12 150 000 + $1 093 500 000 = $1 105 786 500</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Just for one month!</div>\r\n\r\n<div>If you earn $1 200 000 000 or more for just one month, then you successfully reach the challenge 3!</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Reward: $3 000 000 towards the purchase of a luxury car, house, boat et...</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Want to take the money cash? Please, see conditions!</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>There are termes and conditions governing these challenges.</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>For an explanation in a video, please <a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/user-academy/view/48\">click here</a>!</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>', 1, 1, 'PAGE', 'NO SIDEBAR', '2018-11-14 21:08:42', '2019-07-24 02:28:30', 'en'),
