(38, 'PUBLISHED', NULL, 'Distributor', 'distributor', '<p><em><strong>This site is in 2 languages: English and French. To change the site into English or French, click&nbsp;the language name at the top of the page and read carefully the page below to proceed!</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>Save this page! You will need to come back to this page! Save it now! Done! Then proceed please!</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>You need to follow a training right here online before registering in the system: DNAsbook Distributor&nbsp;Training</strong>, it is also called <strong>Opportunity &quot;4&quot;&nbsp;Distributor&nbsp;Training</strong>, you can also call it <strong>DNAsbook Entreprneurship Distributor Training</strong> (its cost is <strong>$25</strong>). It a <strong>4h 57mn</strong> Training online.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>DNAsbook General, LLC</strong> is an entrepreneurship training and financing company based in America. To be a distributor of its training and funding (<strong>Opportunity &ldquo;4&rdquo;</strong>), follow the&nbsp;instructions &nbsp;below,&nbsp;no special level of education is required. Here are the conditions to fulfill to be qualified:</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>1) You can be from any country provided you speak or understand English or French (one of our 2 languages ‚Äã‚Äãused at Opportunity 4 for the moment).</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>2) Be able to go in front of people and talk to them in a convincing way. Communication and explanation skills are required.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>3) <strong>There is a mandatory training:</strong> Before you can have access to our system, you must go through an online training (required). We think you just cannot distribute something you don&rsquo;t understand!</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>4) Apply our&nbsp;<strong>Rule 20/20</strong> (this is mandatory for Opportunity 4 to pay your monthly fees for you through your monthly commissions).</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>5) Your information on your Opportunity &ldquo;4&rdquo; account must be true, accurate and always updated. In case of false information, you will be solely responsible for any errors resulting from it, for example in the case of your commissions being sent to a wrong address or in the case of being not able to communicate with you through email or phone. Opportunity &ldquo;4&rdquo; will not be responsible for such errors if they are due to you, if you choose&nbsp;to put wrong and false information on your account or not updating your account information.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>Important:</strong> You pay <strong>$25</strong>&nbsp;for the online training. On the <a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/dnasbook-distributor-payment?id=2\">next page</a>, you are going to have access to our different methods you can use to pay us. </em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>1) If you choose to pay us through the <strong>1st group of methods</strong> of payment <strong>(PAYING US THROUGH A PHYSICAL FINANCIAL INSTITUTION&nbsp;(In Person Manual Payment))</strong>, this is what happens: After you pay the&nbsp;<strong>$25</strong>&nbsp;for the training, you have to send us your payment information (<strong>Your name, Country, payment receip</strong>t) <strong>to +1 908 249 7637 (USA) on WhatSapp or to the email&nbsp;dnasbookdistributortraining@gmail.com.</strong> In <strong>24 hours</strong>, you will receive <strong>a special code</strong> from our Administration that you will enter on <a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/videos?id=2\">this page</a>&nbsp;(click <a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/videos?id=2\">here</a> to access <a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/videos?id=2\">the page</a>) in the <strong>2nd code field</strong> to access your DNAsbook Distributor Training. Remember, this code lasts <strong>only 72 hours</strong>, if you don&#39;t go through the registration process from the time you enter the code on <a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/videos?id=2\">this page</a> (click <a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/videos?id=2\">here</a> to access <a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/videos?id=2\">that page</a>) in the <strong>2nd code field</strong> to <strong>72 hours (3 days)</strong>, the code expires automatically, you will have to buy a new code for <strong>72 hours</strong> to be able to register.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>2) If you choose to pay us through PayPal, this is what happens:&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Using PayPal&nbsp;to pay your fee allows you to have an automatic and instant access to the Opportunity &quot;4&quot; Distributor Training, you won&#39;t have to wait for us to send you a code. To use the PayPal&nbsp;payment method, you have to pay us through PayPal on&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/dnasbook-distributor-payment?id=2\">this page</a>&nbsp;(click <a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/dnasbook-distributor-payment?id=2\">here</a> to access <a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/dnasbook-distributor-payment?id=2\">the page</a>) at the bottom of <a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/dnasbook-distributor-payment?id=2\">the&nbsp;page</a>, through the &quot;<strong>Pay Now</strong>&quot; button.The training cost is <strong>$25</strong>. What happens when you pay us through PayPal?</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>a)&nbsp;The token field on&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/dnasbook-distributor-payment?id=2\">this page</a>,&nbsp;at the bottom of&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/dnasbook-distributor-payment?id=2\">the page</a>, will be filled automatically with your PayPal token&nbsp;generated by your payment.&nbsp;2)&nbsp;Copy that PayPal token, save it jealously somewhere.&nbsp;3)&nbsp;</em><em>Now go to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/videos?id=2\">this page</a>&nbsp;(click&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/videos?id=2\">here</a>&nbsp;to access&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/videos?id=2\">the page</a>), at the bottom of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/videos?id=2\">the page</a>&nbsp;and paste your PayPal token into&nbsp;the&nbsp;<strong>1st Code field</strong>&nbsp;(the token code field).&nbsp;4)&nbsp;Submit the token to our system&nbsp;by clicking the&nbsp;&quot;<strong>Submit Code</strong>&quot;&nbsp;button&nbsp;to begin watching your training video!</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>Important</strong>:&nbsp;PayPal tokens last&nbsp;only&nbsp;<strong>72 hours&nbsp;</strong>on our site, this means&nbsp;you have&nbsp;<strong>72 hours</strong>&nbsp;to finish the registration process from the time you click&nbsp;&quot;<strong>Submit Code</strong>&quot; button&nbsp;the&nbsp;<strong>1st time</strong>&nbsp;to send your PayPal token into our system. If for any reason, you don&#39;t finish your registration before&nbsp;<strong>72 hours (3 days)</strong>, you will have to buy another PayPal token to be able to finish your registration process.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>What is in this registration process:</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>1) <strong>Payment</strong> (<strong>$25</strong>).</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>2) <strong>DNAsbook Distributor Online Training 4h 57mns).</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>3)&nbsp;<strong>An online profisciency test</strong> (Take notes when going through the video of the&nbsp;training).</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>4) <strong>A Certificate</strong>&nbsp;(After the test, you are given a profiscency Certificate that certifies you as a Distributor of DNAsbook Entrepreneurship Training).</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>5) <strong>Registration</strong> (Registration gives you access to our whole system).</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>After registration, keep your username and password&nbsp;safe. Your affiliate link is very important. Copy your affiliate link and save it. You will see your affiliate link on your dashboard, just above the welcome video. Keep your affiliate link jealously because it is that link you will use to register people into your group as the training will clearly show&nbsp;you. Please, click &quot;next&quot; to proceed!</strong></em></p>', 1, 1, 'PAGE', 'NO SIDEBAR', '2019-06-26 16:54:03', '2019-11-21 16:34:20', 'en'),
(42, 'PUBLISHED', NULL, 'Distributor Training', 'videos', '<p><em><strong>THE CODE PAGE</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>HOW TO USE THIS PAGE?</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>The&nbsp;2 Code fields below will allow you to access your Training! How to use them?</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>1) HOW TO USE THE FIRST CODE FIELD BELOW?</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>a) <strong>The first Code Field</strong> is for <strong>PayPal payment</strong> (the automatic access to the Opportunity &quot;4&quot; Distributor Training). To use that Code Field, you have to pay us through PayPal on <a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/dnasbook-distributor-payment?id=2\">this page</a>,&nbsp;at the botton of this page (click <a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/dnasbook-distributor-payment?id=2\">here</a> to access <a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/dnasbook-distributor-payment?id=2\">the&nbsp;page</a>).&nbsp;<strong>The training cost is $25</strong>. After your payment through PayPal, the token field on <a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/dnasbook-distributor-payment?id=2\">this page</a>, at the bottom of <a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/dnasbook-distributor-payment?id=2\">this page</a> (click <a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/dnasbook-distributor-payment?id=2\">here</a> to access <a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/dnasbook-distributor-payment?id=2\">the page</a>) will be filled automatically with your PayPal token&nbsp;generated by your payment. Copy that PayPal token, save it jealously somewhere.&nbsp;</em><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Come back to this page&nbsp;<strong>below, on this current page,</strong>&nbsp;and paste your PayPal token into <strong>the 1st field (the token code field)</strong>. Submit the token to our site by clicking the <strong>&quot;Submit Code&quot; button</strong> to begin watching your training video!</em><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>Important:</strong> PayPal tokens last <strong>only 72 hours</strong> on our site, this means you have <strong>72 hours </strong>to finish the registration process from the time you click <strong>&quot;Submit Code&quot; button</strong> for <strong>the 1st time</strong> to send your PayPal token into our system. If for any reason, you don&#39;t finish your registration before <strong>72 hours (3 days)</strong>, you will have to buy another PayPal token to be able to finish your registration process.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong>2) HOW TO USE THE SECOND CODE FIELD BELOW?</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>You use <strong>the second Code Field</strong> below if you pay use through the payment methods (banks, Western Union, RIA etc...) on <a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/dnasbook-distributor-payment?id=2\">this page</a>&nbsp;(click <a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/dnasbook-distributor-payment?id=2\">here</a> to access <a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/dnasbook-distributor-payment?id=2\">the page</a>)</em>.<em>&nbsp;How it works?&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>a) <strong>Purchase a Code</strong> from Opportunity &quot;4&quot; Administration by paying <strong>$25</strong> via one of the payment methods offered on <a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/dnasbook-distributor-payment?id=2\">this page</a>&nbsp;(click <a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/dnasbook-distributor-payment?id=2\">here</a> to access <a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/dnasbook-distributor-payment?id=2\">the page</a>).</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>b) <strong>Send us your payment information</strong> (your name, your country, the means used to pay us (bank, Western Union, Ria, etc.) and the payment receipt) at <strong>+1 908 249 7637 (USA) on WhatSapp or at dnasbookdistributortraining@gmail.com.</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>Instantly</strong> or within <strong>24 hours</strong>, you will receive <strong>a special Code</strong> from our administration. Once you have the Code, come back to this page, at the bottom of this page, paste your Code&nbsp;into the <strong>Second Code Field </strong>below, click &quot;<strong>Submit Code</strong>&quot; button to get access to the Opportunity &quot;4&quot; Distributor Training.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>Important:</strong> Remember that this Code <strong>only lasts 72 hours</strong>. If you do not complete the registration process from the moment you enter the Code in the <strong>Second Code Field </strong>below to <strong>72 hours (3 days)</strong>, the Code will<strong> expire automatically</strong>, you will need to purchase <strong>a new 72 hour Code</strong>&nbsp;to be able to continue registration.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, 1, 'PAGE', 'NO SIDEBAR', '2019-07-12 20:03:18', '2019-11-15 21:42:38', 'en'),
