(44, 'PUBLISHED', NULL, 'How to use our sites', 'how-to-use-our-sites', '<p>How to use our two sites?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Why 2 sites? Primarily, Opportunity &quot;4&quot; was put together for Africa, it was later that we extended the project to the whole world. It is why we have 2 sites. One site is for Africa which uses CFA as currency and the second site is for the rest of the world which uses american dollar. The 2 sites are very identical. They fonction the same. The main difference is the currencies.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The objective of Opportunity &quot;4&quot; is to train its subcribers in entrepreneurship and finance them for free. The training is online, it is a life time training. Where do you find this training? Where is the training center on the site? It is under &quot;My Academy&quot;. The courses are in 2 forms: Videos and Texts. Match videos and their text courses to understand well the lessons. Videos and Texts are going to be added to the Academy Center continuously.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The 2 sites have some wonderful features. We have a page for you that you can use for multiple purposes to attract subcribers to your group. Make sure you use it fully. Watch the corresponding video to know how to use this page, it has some amazing features.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We have also a communication center on the site. This center allows you to communicate with your subscribers. Communication is very important in business, specially in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our sites are where you as a subcriber,&nbsp;will do many things, then don&#39;t leave the site, visit your account daily to see what is new, specially in the training center under &quot;My Academy&quot;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, 1, 'PAGE', 'NO SIDEBAR', '2019-08-20 02:06:37', '2019-08-21 17:21:39', 'en'),
(45, 'PUBLISHED', NULL, 'Comment utiliser nos sites', 'comment-utiliser-nos-sites', '<p>Comment utiliser nos deux sites?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Pourquoi 2 sites? En premier lieu, Opportunity &quot;4&quot; a &eacute;t&eacute; cr&eacute;&eacute;e pour l&rsquo;Afrique. C&rsquo;est ensuite que nous avons &eacute;tendu le projet au monde entier. C&#39;est pourquoi nous avons 2 sites. L&#39;un des sites est destin&eacute; &agrave; l&#39;Afrique, qui utilise le franc CFA comme devise, et le second, au reste du monde, utilisant le dollar am&eacute;ricain. Les 2 sites sont tr&egrave;s identiques. Ils fonctionnent de la m&ecirc;me mani&egrave;re. La principale diff&eacute;rence r&eacute;side dans les monnaies.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>L&rsquo;opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot; a pour objectif de former ses souscripteurs dans&nbsp;l&rsquo;entrepreneuriat et les financer gratuitement. La formation est en ligne, c&#39;est une formation &agrave; vie. O&ugrave; trouvez-vous cette formation? O&ugrave; se trouve le centre de formation sur nos&nbsp;sites? C&#39;est sous &quot;Mon Acad&eacute;mie&quot;. Les cours sont sous 2 formes: vid&eacute;os et textes. Comparez les vid&eacute;os et leurs cours en&nbsp;textes pour bien comprendre les le&ccedil;ons. Des vid&eacute;os et des textes seront ajout&eacute;s en permanence au centre de l&#39;Acad&eacute;mie.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Les 2 sites ont de merveilleuses fonctionnalit&eacute;s. Nous avons une page pour vous que vous pouvez utiliser &agrave; plusieurs fins pour attirer les souscripteurs dans&nbsp;votre groupe. Assurez-vous de l&#39;utiliser pleinement. Regardez la vid&eacute;o correspondante pour savoir comment utiliser cette page, elle poss&egrave;de des fonctionnalit&eacute;s &eacute;tonnantes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nous avons &eacute;galement un centre de communication sur le site. Ce centre vous permet de communiquer avec vos abonn&eacute;s. La communication est tr&egrave;s importante dans les affaires, sp&eacute;cialement dans Opportunity &quot;4&quot;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nos sites vous permettent, en tant qu&#39;abonn&eacute;, de faire beaucoup de choses, alors ne quittez pas le site, consultez votre compte tous les jours pour voir les nouveaut&eacute;s, en particulier dans le Centre de formation situ&eacute; sous &quot;Mon Acad&eacute;mie&quot;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, 1, 'PAGE', 'NO SIDEBAR', '2019-08-20 02:08:13', '2019-08-21 17:26:42', 'fr'),
(46, 'PUBLISHED', NULL, 'How Opportunity 4 works', 'how-opportunity-4-works', '<p>How Opportunity &quot;4&quot; works?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Opportunity &quot;4&quot; is an entrepreneurship network that trains its subscribers into entrepreneurs and finances them for free. Then, there are 2 mains sections in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;: Training and Financing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>How it works?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Who wants to participate into Opportunity &quot;4&quot; must subscribe on our site and follow online our training. Where this training is located on our sites? Under &quot;My Academy&quot;. This training is in 2 forms: Videos and texts. Compare and match the 2 forms for better understanding of our lessons.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>How we finance you while training you in entrepreneurship online?&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After registration, you have an affiliate link on your dashboard, this affiliate link is very important for you, it allows you to subscribe people into your group.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>How it works?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We have 4 levels of benefits in Opportunity &quot;4&quot; to help our subscribers maximize their commissions in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;. To subscribe people at your first level, you have to give your affiliate link to them. When they open it in an internet browser, the link becomes a registration page, when they register on that registration page generated by your affiliate link, they are placed at your 1st level. When they give their affliate links to other people who register on them, those people are placed at your 2nd level. When people on your 2nd level give their affiliate links to other people who register on them, they are placed at your 3rd level. When subscribers at your 3rd level give their affliate links to people and they register on them, they are placed at your 4th level. The system stops your growth in high at the 4th level, but when subscribers on your 4 levels continue bringing other people into the system, your group will continue growing indefinately in large.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>How are you paid on all these subscribers?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There is a monthly fee subcribers pay into the system. We pay you 40% on the total of the fees all the subscribers on your 4 levels of benefit pay into the system every month. Because there are 4 levels, at every level, you are paid 10% of the total of the fees subscribers pay on that level.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Why 4 levels of benefits in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;? It is to explose your commissions. Watch the corresponding video to see how this works!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, 1, 'PAGE', 'NO SIDEBAR', '2019-08-20 03:20:46', '2019-08-21 17:44:30', 'en'),
(47, 'PUBLISHED', NULL, 'Comment fonctionne Opportunity 4', 'comment-fonctionne-opportunity-4', '<p>Comment Opportunity &quot;4&quot; fonctionne?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Opportunity &quot;4&quot; est un r&eacute;seau d&rsquo;entrepreneurship qui forme ses abonn&eacute;s en entrepreneurs et les finance gratuitement. Il y a 2 sections principales dans Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot;: Formation et financement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Comment &ccedil;a marche?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Qui veut participer dans Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot; doit s&#39;inscrire sur notre site et suivre en ligne notre formation. O&ugrave; se trouve cette formation sur nos sites? Sous &quot;Mon Acad&eacute;mie&quot;. Cette formation se pr&eacute;sente sous 2 formes: vid&eacute;os et textes. Comparez&nbsp;les 2 formes pour une meilleure compr&eacute;hension de nos le&ccedil;ons.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Comment on vous finance pendant que nous&nbsp;vous formons&nbsp;en entrepreneuriat en ligne?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Apr&egrave;s votre inscription, vous avez un lien d&#39;affiliation sur votre tableau de bord. Ce lien d&#39;affiliation est tr&egrave;s important pour vous. Il vous permet d&#39;inscrire des personnes dans votre groupe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Comment &ccedil;a marche?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nous avons 4 niveaux d&#39;avantages dans Opportunity &quot;4&quot; pour aider nos abonn&eacute;s &agrave; maximiser leurs commissions dans Opportunity &quot;4&quot;. Pour inscrire des personnes &agrave; votre premier niveau, vous devez leur donner votre lien d&rsquo;affiliation. Lorsqu&#39;ils l&#39;ouvrent dans un navigateur Internet, le lien devient une page d&#39;inscription. Lorsqu&#39;ils s&#39;enregistrent sur cette page d&#39;enregistrement g&eacute;n&eacute;r&eacute;e par votre lien d&#39;affili&eacute;, ils sont plac&eacute;s &agrave; votre 1er niveau. Lorsqu&#39;ils donnent leurs liens d&#39;affiliation &agrave; d&#39;autres personnes qui s&#39;y inscrivent, ces personnes sont plac&eacute;es &agrave; votre 2e niveau. Lorsque les personnes de votre deuxi&egrave;me niveau donnent leurs liens d&rsquo;affiliation &agrave; d&rsquo;autres personnes qui s&rsquo;y inscrivent, elles sont plac&eacute;es &agrave; votre troisi&egrave;me niveau. Lorsque les abonn&eacute;s de votre 3&egrave;me niveau donnent leurs liens affili&eacute;s &agrave; des personnes et s&rsquo;y inscrivent, ils sont plac&eacute;s &agrave; votre 4&egrave;me niveau. Le syst&egrave;me arr&ecirc;te votre croissance en hauteur au 4&egrave;me niveau, mais lorsque les abonn&eacute;s de vos 4 niveaux continuent d&#39;introduire d&#39;autres personnes dans le syst&egrave;me, votre groupe continuera &agrave; s&#39;agrandir&nbsp;ind&eacute;finiment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Comment &ecirc;tes-vous pay&eacute; sur tous ces abonn&eacute;s?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Les abonn&eacute;s paient des frais mensuels dans le syst&egrave;me. Nous vous payons 40% sur le total des frais que tous les abonn&eacute;s de vos 4 niveaux&nbsp;paient&nbsp;dans le syst&egrave;me chaque mois. Comme il y a 4 niveaux, &agrave; chaque niveau, vous recevez 10% du total des frais que les abonn&eacute;s paient &agrave;&nbsp;ce niveau.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Pourquoi 4 niveaux de b&eacute;n&eacute;fices dans Opportunity &quot;4&quot;? C&#39;est pour exploser vos commissions. Regardez la vid&eacute;o correspondante pour voir comment cela fonctionne.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, 1, 'PAGE', 'NO SIDEBAR', '2019-08-20 03:22:39', '2019-08-21 17:45:52', 'fr'),
(48, 'PUBLISHED', NULL, 'How to earn the 842 100 US dollars at the end of the 5th month', 'how-to-earn-the-842-100-us-dollars-at-the-end-of-the-5th-month', '<p>How to earn the 842 100 US dollars&nbsp;at the end of the 5th month? It is by applying Rule 20/20. How?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Applying Rule 20/20 means that after registration, you have to subscribe 20 people under you through your affiliate link preferrably in your 1st month. While you are subscribing each of your 1st 20 people, you must ask them to apply Rule 20/20 too, they have to subscribe into the system, each of them, &nbsp;in their 1st 30 days 20 people through their affiliate links and ask their subscribers to do the same, preferrably, in their 1st 30 days.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In conclusion, aqpplying Rule 20/20 in Opportunity &quot;4&quot; means each subscriber must subscribe into the system 20 people, preferrably in the 1st 30 days and ask those 20 people to do the same in the 1st 30 days and pass the message and the training to their subscribers too.<br />\r\nIf this is done, what happens?&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>By subscribing into the system 20 people in your 1st 30 days, even if you stop subscribing people into the system but you apply Rule 20/20, at the end of the second month you must have 400 people in your account. By the end of the 3rd month you must have 8000 people in your account. By the end of the 4th month, you must have 160 000 people in your account. If in your group everybody pays their monthly fees regularly in the system, we pay you at the end of every month 40% of the total of the fees collected in your group. Because we have 4 levels of benefit in every group, we pay you 10% of the total of the fees at every level, this is the way you earn $842 100&nbsp;at the end of the 5th month.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As you can see it, that amount is a strict minimum when you strictly apply Rule 20/20. Imagine that after you bring into the system 20 people and ask them to subscribe also 20 people into the