(60, 'PUBLISHED', NULL, 'Why taxes are not included in commissions calculation', 'why-taxes-are-not-included-in-commissions-calculation', '<p>Why we don\'t mention the taxes in our calculations of the commissions?<br></p><p>We don\'t mention or use the taxes with the base fees in the calculation of subscribers commissions besauce taxes go the government, we don\'t pocket these taxes as company.<br></p><p>We do know that we need to pay these taxes for the goverment to continue doing or delivering the important public services we dearly need. Don\'t tell me you don\'t know these important services! Ok, let me refresh your mind: Government creates for us schools, hospitals, makes roads ect... things and services we cannot afford on ourselves. Taxes have to be paid for these important&nbsp;things to be taken care of by the government.&nbsp;<br></p><p>And when you pay taxes, you don\'t claim them back unless you are in USA where some fractions of the taxes are clained at the end of the year by some qualified workers if you don\'t fall into the category where they ask you to pay more money at the end of the year.<br></p><p>Conclusion: Taxes go to the government, we don\'t packet them, it is why we don\'t includ them in the calculation of the suscribers commissions.</p><p><br></p>', 1, 1, 'PAGE', NULL, '2019-09-02 03:04:46', '2019-09-02 03:04:46', 'en'),
(61, 'PUBLISHED', NULL, 'Pourquoi ne mentionnons-nous pas les taxes dans nos calculs des commissions', 'pourquoi-ne-mentionnons-nous-pas-les-taxes-dans-nos-calculs-des-commissions', '<p>Pourquoi ne mentionnons-nous pas les taxes dans nos calculs des commissions?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nous n&#39;incluons pas&nbsp;les taxes&nbsp;dans le calcul des commissions des abonn&eacute;s&nbsp;parce que&nbsp;les taxes vont au gouvernement, elles ne nous appartiennent pas.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nous savons que nous devons payer ces taxes pour que le gouvernement puisse continuer&nbsp;&agrave; fournir les services publics importants dont nous avons tant&nbsp;besoin. Ne me dites pas que vous ne connaissez pas ces services importants! Ok, laissez-moi vous rafra&icirc;chir la la m&eacute;moire: le gouvernement cr&eacute;e pour nous des &eacute;coles, des h&ocirc;pitaux, des routes&nbsp;etc...&nbsp;des choses et des services que nous ne pouvons pas nous payer nous-m&ecirc;me. Les imp&ocirc;ts doivent &ecirc;tre pay&eacute;s pour que ces choses importantes soient prises en charge par le gouvernement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Et lorsque vous payez des imp&ocirc;ts, vous ne les r&eacute;clamez pas &agrave; moins que vous soyiez&nbsp;aux &Eacute;tats-Unis&nbsp;o&ugrave; des fractions des imp&ocirc;ts sont r&eacute;clam&eacute;es&nbsp;&agrave; la fin de l&rsquo;ann&eacute;e par des travailleurs qualifi&eacute;s si vous ne tombez pas dans la cat&eacute;gorie o&ugrave; ils vous&nbsp;demandent de&nbsp;payer plus d&#39;argent &agrave; la fin de l&#39;ann&eacute;e.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Conclusion: les taxes sont vers&eacute;es au gouvernement, nous ne les reclamons&nbsp;pas, c&#39;est pourquoi nous ne les incluons pas dans le calcul des commissions des abonn&eacute;s.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, 1, 'PAGE', 'NO SIDEBAR', '2019-09-02 03:07:05', '2019-09-02 03:27:19', 'fr'),
(62, 'PUBLISHED', NULL, 'Do not waste your time after registration', 'do-not-waste-your-time-after-registration', '<p>How to avoid wasting time after registration?<br></p><p>To avoid wasting time after you register, you need to know this thing: Opportunity \"4\" is put together to help subscribers financially, and through them, help other people financially, then it is not your&nbsp;money which is asked in Opportunity \"4\", it is you inviting other people into the system that is the key of success in Opportunity \"4\".</p><p>You need to do 2 things after registration:<br>1) Apply Rule 20/20 subscribing 20 people into the system through your affiliate link.<br>2) Ask these 20 people to subscribe also into the system through their affiliate links 20 people and ask them to do the same thing.</p><p>If you make sure this message passes from subscriber to subscriber till your 4th level and you educate subscribers in your group that they need to pay their monthly fees (your monthly commissions come from the monthly fees of the subscribers in your group), we promise you a growth in Opportunity \"4\" you won\'t believe!<br></p><p>This is the secret of succeeding quickly in Opportunity \"4\"! Emphasize is put on inviting people into the system and help them invite other people into the system applying Rule 20/20 and make sure monthly fees are paid on time. Why? Your monthly commissions come from these fees.<br></p><p><br></p><p>Why monthly fees in Opportunity \"4\"? Because we train you in entrepreneurship and finance you. You are paying a service (training and financing) we are rendering to you.<br>The good news for you is we decide not to keep all these fees for ourselves, we pay you 40% of these fees if you invite other people into the system.</p><p><br></p>', 1, 1, 'PAGE', NULL, '2019-09-02 21:37:11', '2019-09-02 21:37:11', 'en'),
