al dans&nbsp;notre syst&egrave;me en cliquant sur le bouton &quot;<strong>Soumettez&nbsp;le code</strong>&quot; pour commencer &agrave; regarder votre vid&eacute;o de formation!</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>Important:</strong>&nbsp;Les Jetons PayPal ne durent que <strong>72 heures</strong> sur notre site. Cela signifie que vous avez <strong>72 heures</strong> pour terminer le processus d&rsquo;enregistrement &agrave; partir du moment o&ugrave; vous cliquez sur le bouton &quot;<strong>Soumettez&nbsp;le Code</strong>&quot; pour la premi&egrave;re fois que vous envoyez votre Jeton PayPal dans notre syst&egrave;me. Si, pour une raison quelconque, vous ne terminez pas votre inscription avant <strong>72 heures (3 jours)</strong>, vous devrez acheter un autre Jeton PayPal pour pouvoir terminer votre processus d&#39;inscription.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Si vous &ecirc;tes pr&ecirc;t, allez-y et cliquez sur le bouton de paiement ci-dessous!</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, 1, 'PAGE', 'NO SIDEBAR', '2019-09-09 02:31:49', '2019-11-20 23:48:32', 'fr'),
(70, 'PUBLISHED', NULL, 'DNAsbook Webinar Questions', 'dnasbook-webinar-questions', '<p><strong><em>Notes</em>:</strong>&nbsp;<em>You have to answer correctly the following questions before proceeding if not, the page will be blocked.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>&nbsp;<br />\r\nAfter the choice of your answers, click the button &quot;<strong>Submit</strong>&quot;. If your answers are correct, there will be&nbsp;<strong>a green message</strong>&nbsp;asking you to click &quot;next&quot; button to proceed. If there are <strong>some&nbsp;mistakes</strong>&nbsp;in your answers, <strong>the page will be&nbsp;blocked</strong>&nbsp;till you chose the correct answers.&nbsp;</em><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>If you cannot find the correct answers (that means you did not pay enough attention during the training), go back to the video and watch it more carefully this time when taking notes. The questions are not difficult, we are just looking for <strong>a basic understanding</strong> of Opportunity &quot;4&quot; from you before giving you a certificate and allowing you to be a <strong>Distributor</strong> of the training.&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>THE QUESTIONS TO ANSWER</strong></h4>', 1, 1, 'PAGE', 'NO SIDEBAR', '2019-09-09 02:42:38', '2019-11-17 18:25:48', 'en'),
(71, 'PUBLISHED', NULL, 'Questioonaires de Webinaire de DNAsbook', 'dnasbook-webinar-questions', '<p><strong><em>Remarques</em>:</strong>&nbsp;<em>Vous devez r&eacute;pondre correctement aux questions suivantes avant de proc&eacute;der sinon, la page sera bloqu&eacute;e.</em><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Apr&egrave;s le choix de vos r&eacute;ponses, cliquez sur le bouton &quot;<strong>Submit</strong>&quot;. Si vos r&eacute;ponses sont correctes, <strong>un&nbsp;message vert</strong>&nbsp;vous invitera &agrave; cliquer sur le bouton &quot;Next&quot; pour continuer. S&#39;il y a des erreurs dans vos r&eacute;ponses, la page sera bloqu&eacute;e jusqu&#39;&agrave; ce que vous choisissiez les bonnes r&eacute;ponses.</em><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Si vous ne trouvez pas les <strong>vraies r&eacute;ponses</strong>&nbsp;(cela signifie que vous n&rsquo;aviez pas fait suffisamment attention au cours de la formation), retournez &agrave; la vid&eacute;o,&nbsp;regardez-la plus attentivement cette fois-ci pendant que&nbsp;vous prenez d<strong>es notes</strong>. Les questions ne sont pas difficiles, nous recherchons simplement que vous ayiez <strong>une compr&eacute;hension de base de Opportunity &quot;4&quot;&nbsp;</strong>avant de vous donner un certificat et vous permettre d&#39;&ecirc;tre un&nbsp;<strong>Distributeur agr&eacute;&eacute;</strong>&nbsp;de la Formation.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>VOICI LES QUESTIONS &Agrave; R&Eacute;PONDRE</strong></h4>', 1, 1, 'PAGE', 'NO SIDEBAR', '2019-09-09 02:43:58', '2019-11-17 18:29:13', 'fr'),
(72, 'PUBLISHED', NULL, 'DNAsbook Distributor Training Certificate', 'dnasbook-distributor-training-certificate', '<p>Congratulations! You have passed your <em><strong>Opportunity &quot;4&quot; Distributor Training Test</strong></em>!&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fill the form below to be able to print your Certificate on the next page!&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<form action=\"/pages/certificate?id=\" method=\"post\">\r\n<div class=\"form-group\">\r\n      <label class=\"control-label col-sm-2\" for=\"name\">Name:</label>\r\n      <div class=\"col-sm-4\">\r\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\" id=\"name\" placeholder=\"Enter name\" name=\"name\" required>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n <div class=\"form-group\">\r\n      <label class=\"control-label col-sm-2\" for=\"email\">Email:</label>\r\n      <div class=\"col-sm-4\">\r\n        <input type=\"email\" class=\"form-control\" id=\"email\" placeholder=\"Enter email\" name=\"email\" required>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\r\n      <label class=\"control-label col-sm-2\" for=\"Country\">Country:</label>\r\n      <div class=\"col-sm-4\">          \r\n        <input type=\"Country\" class=\"form-control\" id=\"Country\" placeholder=\"Enter Country\" name=\"Country\" required>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n<div class=\"text\">\r\n\r\n<p>After you print your certificate on the next page, we will allow you to register in the system, have access to your affiliate link on your dashboard and begin registering people into your group! That will be the beginning of your route towards your financial independance!</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong><input type=\"submit\" id=\"next-page\" value=\"NEXT PAGE\"/>&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;</strong></em></p>\r\n</form>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, 1, 'PAGE', 'NO SIDEBAR', '2019-09-09 02:45:39', '2019-09-12 01:07:49', 'en'),
(73, 'PUBLISHED', NULL, 'Certificat de Fin de Formation de Distributeur', 'dnasbook-distributor-training-certificate', '<p>Toutes nos f&eacute;licitations! Vous avez r&eacute;ussi votre test de Formation de Distributeur de Opportunity &quot;4&quot;!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Remplissez le formulaire ci-dessous pour pouvoir imprimer votre certificat sur&nbsp;la page suivante!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<form action=\"/pages/certificate?id=\" method=\"post\">\r\n<div class=\"form-group\">\r\n      <label class=\"control-label col-sm-2\" for=\"name\">Votre Nom:</label>\r\n      <div class=\"col-sm-4\">\r\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\" id=\"name\" placeholder=\"\r\nentrez le nom\" name=\"name\" required>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n <div class=\"form-group\">\r\n      <label class=\"control-label col-sm-2\" for=\"email\">Votre Email:</label>\r\n      <div class=\"col-sm-4\">\r\n        <input type=\"email\" class=\"form-control\" id=\"email\" placeholder=\"entrer email\" name=\"email\" required>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\r\n      <label class=\"control-label col-sm-2\" for=\"Country\">Votre Pays:</label>\r\n      <div class=\"col-sm-4\">          \r\n        <input type=\"Country\" class=\"form-control\" id=\"Country\" placeholder=\"entrer pays\" name=\"Country\" required>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n<div class=\"text\">\r\n<p>Apr&egrave;s avoir imprim&eacute; votre certificat sur la page suivante, nous vous permettrons de vous inscrire dans le syst&egrave;me, d&rsquo;avoir acc&egrave;s &agrave; votre lien d&rsquo;affiliation sur votre Tableau de Bord et de commencer &agrave; inscrire des gens&nbsp;dans votre groupe! Ce sera le d&eacute;but de votre parcours vers votre ind&eacute;pendance financi&egrave;re!&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div\r\n<p><em><strong><input type=\"submit\" id=\"next-page\" value=\"PAGE SUIVANTE\"/>&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;</strong></em></p>\r\n</form>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, 1, 'PAGE', 'NO SIDEBAR', '2019-09-