(88, 'PUBLISHED', NULL, 'There Is A Mandatory Training To Follow', 'there-is-a-mandatory-training-to-follow', '<p><em><strong>Read carefully the page below to proceed!&nbsp;</strong></em><em><strong>Save this page! You will need to come back to this page! Save it now! Done! Then proceed please!</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>How do you begin earning money TODAY in Opportunity &quot;4&quot; and the big money later, just after ONE month? Below are the simple steps to follow:</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>1)&nbsp;</em><em>You need to follow a training right here online (the training will cost you <strong>$25</strong>) and&nbsp;register&nbsp;in our&nbsp;system!</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>2) Sell registration to interested people (we allow you to earn money TODAY by selling OUR registration to interested people and take the money for yourself).</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>3) When making money by selling our registration to interested people, something amazing is happening: You are subscribing people into your group that will help you make unbelievable amounts of money just from&nbsp;the next month following your registration.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>4) Your unbelievable amounts of money in forms of monthly commissions will be a lifetime earnings, more subscribers you have at your 4 levels, more monthly commissions you earn and this increases indefinately....&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>First of all, let me tell you a little bit about Opportunity &quot;4&quot;!</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>Opportunity &quot;4&quot; is a part of DNAsbook General, LLC,</strong>&nbsp;an entrepreneurship training and financing company based in America. To be a distributor of its training and funding (<strong>Opportunity &ldquo;4&rdquo;</strong>), you just have to follow instructions we are going to give you, there is no special level of education required. Here are the conditions to fulfill to be qualified:</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>1) There is no discrimination at Opportunity &quot;4&quot;. You can be from any country provided you speak or understand English or French (one of our 2 languages ‚Äã‚Äãused at Opportunity 4 for the moment).</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>2) Be able to go in front of people and talk to them in a convincing way. Communication and explanation skills are required.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>3) <strong>There is a mandatory training </strong>(<strong>4h 57mns</strong>)<strong>:</strong> Before you can have access to our system, you must go through an online training (r<strong>equired</strong>). We think you just cannot distribute something you don&rsquo;t understand!</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>4) Apply our&nbsp;<strong>Rule 20/20</strong> (this is mandatory for Opportunity &quot;4&quot; to pay your monthly fees for you through your monthly commissions).</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>5) Your information on your Opportunity &ldquo;4&rdquo; account must be true, accurate and always updated. In case of false information, you will be solely responsible for any errors resulting from it, for example in the case of your commissions being sent to a wrong address or in the case of being not able to communicate with you through email or phone. Opportunity &ldquo;4&rdquo; will not be responsible for such errors if they are due to you, if you choose&nbsp;to put wrong and false information on your account or not updating your account information.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>How do you begin the whole registration?</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>1) You need <strong>a special Code</strong> from Opportunity &quot;4&quot; Office to access our&nbsp;<strong>Online Training&nbsp;</strong>(<strong>4h 57mns</strong>). That code costs you <strong>$25</strong>.&nbsp;On <a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/dnasbook-distributor-payment?id=2\">the next page</a>, you are going to see our different payment methods we offer. Read <a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/dnasbook-distributor-payment?id=2\">them</a>, choose one according to your geographical location. </em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>2)&nbsp; How do you pay the <strong>$25</strong>&nbsp;for the training, and after the payment, what happens?</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>1) If you choose to pay us through the <strong>1st group of methods</strong> of payment <strong>(PAYING US THROUGH A PHYSICAL FINANCIAL INSTITUTION&nbsp;(In Person Manual Payment))</strong>, this is what happens: After you pay the&nbsp;<strong>$25</strong>&nbsp;for the training, you have to send us your payment information (<strong>Your name, Country, payment receip</strong>t) <strong>to +1 908 249 7637 (USA) on WhatSapp or to the email&nbsp;dnasbookdistributortraining@gmail.com.</strong> In <strong>24 hours</strong>, you will receive <strong>a special code</strong> from our Administration that you will enter on <a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/videos?id=2\">this page</a>&nbsp;(click <a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/videos?id=2\">here</a> to access <a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/videos?id=2\">the page</a>) in the <strong>2nd code field</strong> to access your DNAsbook Distributor Training. Remember, this code lasts <strong>only 72 hours</strong>, if you don&#39;t go through the registration process from the time you enter the code on <a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/videos?id=2\">this page</a> (click <a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/videos?id=2\">here</a> to access <a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/videos?id=2\">that page</a>) in the <strong>2nd code field</strong> to <strong>72 hours (3 days)</strong>, the code expires automatically, you will have to buy a new code for <strong>72 hours</strong> to be able to register.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>2) If you choose to pay us through PayPal, this is what happens:&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Using PayPal&nbsp;to pay your fee allows you to have an automatic and instant access to the Opportunity &quot;4&quot; Distributor Training, you won&#39;t have to wait for us to send you a code. To use the PayPal&nbsp;payment method, you have to pay us through PayPal on&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/dnasbook-distributor-payment?id=2\">this page</a>&nbsp;at the bottom of the&nbsp;page, through the &quot;<strong>Pay Now</strong>&quot; button.The training cost is <strong>$25</strong>. What happens when you pay us through PayPal?</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>a)&nbsp;The token field on&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/dnasbook-distributor-payment?id=2\">this page</a>,&nbsp;at the bottom of&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/dnasbook-distributor-payment?id=2\">the page</a>, will be filled automatically with your PayPal token&nbsp;generated by your payment.&nbsp;2)&nbsp;Copy that PayPal token, save it jealously somewhere.&nbsp;3)&nbsp;</em><em>Now go to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/videos?id=2\">this page</a>&nbsp;(click&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/videos?id=2\">here</a>&nbsp;to access&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/videos?id=2\">the page</a>), at the bottom of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.dnasbookdigimarket.com/pages/videos?id=2\">the page</a>&nbsp;and paste your PayPal token into&nbsp;the&nbsp;1st Code field&nbsp;(the token code field).&nbsp;4)&nbsp;Submit the token to our system&nbsp;by clicking the&nbsp;&quot;<strong>Submit Code</strong>&quot;&nbsp;button&nbsp;to begin watching your training video!</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Important:&nbsp;PayPal tokens last&nbsp;only&nbsp;<strong>72 hours&nbsp;</strong>on our site, this means&nbsp;you have&nbsp;<strong>72 hours</strong>&nbsp;to finish the registration process from the time you click&nbsp;&quot;<strong>Submit Code</strong>&quot; button&nbsp;the&nbsp;<strong>1st time</strong>&nbsp;to send your PayPal token into our system. If for any reason, you don&#39;t finish your registration before&nbsp;<strong>72 hours (3 days)</strong>, you will have to buy another PayPal token to be able to finish your registration process.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>What is in this registration process:</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>1) <strong>Payment</strong> (<strong>$25</strong>).</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>2) <strong>DNAsbook Distributor Online Training.</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>3)&nbsp;<strong>An online profisciency test</strong> (Take notes when going through the video of the&nbsp;training).</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>4) <strong>A Certificate</strong>&nbsp;(After the test, you will be&nbsp;given a profiscency Certificate that certifies you as a Distributor of DNAsbook Entrepreneurship Training).</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>5) <strong>Registration</strong> (Registration gives you access to our whole system).</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><em>How do you begin earning real money the very day of your registration in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;?</em></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>1) After the registration process (payment of <strong>$25</strong>, reception of the registration code, completion of the training, printing or saving your pofisciency Certificate, actual registration on our site).</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>2) Copy your <strong>Affiliate Link</strong> from your Dashboard (just at the top of the welcome video on the home page) and save it at a secure place.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>3) Begin selling the registration to interested people. How do you sell the registration?&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>a)&nbsp;Of course, you have to talk to people about this wonderful opportunity. To interested people, give YOUR affiliate link and sell them your <strong>non-expired</strong>&nbsp;code you received from Opportunity &quot;4&quot; Office, they need that non-expired code to access the training video&nbsp;(selling your code to interested people is the 1st way to begin making money in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;. We advise you to sell your code less then <strong>$25</strong>. Why? People will buy it from you quicker and more money you will make).</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>b) Tell the interested people who register through your Affiliate Link and your Code to sell your code along with <strong>THEIR</strong> Affiliate Links to other interested people as long as the code is not expired, this helps you get quickly subscribers in your group and more subscribers you get at your 4 levels, huge commissions you get at the end of the months.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>c) You and the other subscribers in your group should&nbsp;buy new codes from Opportunity &quot;4&quot; Office to sell along with your Affiliate Links to make unlimited money, this will help you pay your monthly fees without using your monthly commissions money. Do you see the scope of the opportunity which is lying here in front of you?</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>Important Note</strong>: No subscriber is allowed to sell <strong>a Code that will expire in less than 10 hours</strong>. Why? The buyer will not have enough time to go through the registration process (<strong>Training (4h 57mns), profiscency test, printing or saving certificate and registration on our site</strong>) before the expiration of the code.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>How do you know when the code is expiring? There is a <strong>Time Clock</strong> that appears automatically at the top of the pages (from the training video page to the registration page) showing <strong>the count down of the 72 hours (3 days)</strong> from the very second the Code was&nbsp;used for the 1st time to open the training video.&nbsp;This Time Clock is shown to all users of the specific code <strong>worldwide</strong>.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>After registration, keep your username and password&nbsp;safe. Your affiliate link is very important. Copy your affiliate link and save it. You will see your affiliate link on your dashboard, just above the welcome video. Keep your affiliate link jealously because it is that link you will use to register people into your group as the training will clearly show&nbsp;you. Please, click &quot;next&quot; to proceed!</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, 1, 'PAGE', 'NO SIDEBAR', '2019-11-13 00:06:44', '2019-11-21 01:01:23', 'en');
